name: Snow - HEN500K edition
description:
A special artwork for the HEN500K event. Time flies in the NFT space, a few months ago we were still in the 10K area. Incredible journey and adventure, lots of fun, frustration and marvels. And let's not forget the amazing community. Thank you all, and let's continue on this rocky road. LFG! WGMI!
